title: DAZ3D - Poser - The Abandoned City 1 and 2 by Stonemason - (1811
description:
The incident occurred over 40 years ago, but the world will forever bear the scars. While most cities were destroyed, some managed to survive the chaos. This city is still standing, but who knows what dangers lie within its borders?

The Abandoned City 1 is a full scene that comes complete with concrete barrier, grass patch, hedge, plant, plants patch, and street lamp.

The Abandoned City 2 is a full scene that comes complete with multiple buildings, paving, a road section, sapling, and tree.
